<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَي الزَّكَاة<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>تتَعَلَّق بِالْمَالِ تعلق شركَة<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
